    "text": "Two suspects arrested for possessing diesel stocks without licenses - Thambalagamuwa Police. On the evening of 2026.04.02, a team of officers from the Thambalagamuwa Police conducted two raids in the Mollipothana area of the Thambalagamuwa Police Division on a tip-off and arrested two suspects who were in possession of 1430 liters of diesel without a license and 615 liters of diesel without a license. The suspects are residents of Trincomalee and Thambalagamuwa areas, aged 41 and 61. Thambalagamuwa Police are conducting further investigations. 05. \u0db1\u0dd3\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dbb\u0ddd\u0db0\u0dd3 \u0db8\u0dad\u0dca \u0dd0\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc3\u0db8\u0d9f \u0dc3\u0dd0 \u0dbb\u0dd4\u0db4\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dd4 \u0d85\u0dad\u0dca\u0d85\u0da9\u0d82\u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dd9\u0da7 - \u0d87\u0dc4\u0dd0\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dba\u0db4\u0d9c\u0ddc\u0da9 \u0db4 \u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dca\u0dae\u0ddc\u0db1\u0dba.",
